; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the error path for unbalanced balanced-virtual postings.
; When [balanced virtual] postings don't sum to zero and there is no
; null posting among them, finalize() throws a balance error.

2024/03/01 Unbalanced Virtuals
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash      $-10.00
    [Budget:Food]     $5.00
    [Budget:Dining]   $3.00

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 10:
While balancing transaction from "$FILE", lines 6-10:
> 2024/03/01 Unbalanced Virtuals
>     Expenses:Food     $10.00
>     Assets:Cash      $-10.00
>     [Budget:Food]     $5.00
>     [Budget:Dining]   $3.00
Unbalanced remainder is:
               $8.00
Amount to balance against:
              $18.00
Error: Transaction does not balance
end test
